justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../duan-shophouse-richmond-city-quan-binh-thanh-29.htmlhttp:/tapdoanhungthinh.vn/duan-shophouse-richmond-city-quan-binh-thanh-29.html\"><img src=\"../media/images/vi-tri-richmond_1.png?1470965569786\" width=\"100%\" /></a></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>ĐĂNG K&Yacute; NGAY NHẬN BẢNG GI&Aacute;&nbsp;SHOPHOUSE</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://sanhungthinh.com/upload/images/animated-arrow.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"47\" height=\"26\" /></strong><a href=\"../duan-saigonmia-trung-son-sky-in-your-eyes-1.html#dangkyxemnha\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../media/images/dang-ky-button.png?1466180235102\" width=\"200\" height=\"76\" /></a></h4>', '<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>A:MẶT BẰNG SHOPHOUSE BLOCK GLORY</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../duan-shophouse-richmond-city-quan-binh-thanh-29.htmlhttp:/tapdoanhungthinh.vn/duan-shophouse-richmond-city-quan-binh-thanh-29.html\"><strong><img src=\"../media/images/richmond-3.jpg?1475050795288\" width=\"100%\" /></strong></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>B:MẶT BẰNG SHOPHOUSE BLOCK RICHRES</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Updating...</strong></span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>ĐĂNG K&Yacute; NGAY NHẬN BẢNG GI&Aacute; SHOPHOUSE</strong></span></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://sanhungthinh.com/upload/images/animated-arrow.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"47\" height=\"26\" /></strong><a href=\"../duan-saigonmia-trung-son-sky-in-your-eyes-1.html#dangkyxemnha\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"../media